name: Chief Chirpa (V)
Lore: 'Leader of Wicket''s Ewok tribe for 42 seasons. Head of the Council of Elders. Decided to spare Han''s Rebels and join their fight against the Empire.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor. Ewoks on Endor are power +1. ''Vehicle with armor'' on Ewok Catapult may be treated as ''non-Dark Jedi character'' (''crashes'' is then treated as ''lost''). May not be targeted by weapons.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
